00:42:25,084 --> 00:42:27,128
- Pak Kim.
- Astaga.

481
00:42:28,630 --> 00:42:31,341
Kau tak tertangkap, Yeong-ro.

482
00:42:32,926 --> 00:42:34,010
Itu bagus!

483
00:42:36,346 --> 00:42:39,182
Kau benar. Dia membawanya masuk.

484
