00:50:21,269 --> 00:50:24,898
Sampai jumpa di Harmony pukul 18.00.

582
00:50:24,981 --> 00:50:26,191
Baiklah.

583
00:50:29,819 --> 00:50:31,738
Astaga!

584
00:50:42,457 --> 00:50:45,126
{\an8}INGIN MENJADI PENYANYI OPERA
