693
00:57:45,839 --> 00:57:47,674
Tentu.

694
00:57:48,591 --> 00:57:49,759
Jangan khawatir.

695
00:57:51,719 --> 00:57:55,765
Apa yang akan kau jadikan barangmu?

696
00:57:56,057 --> 00:57:58,017
